exceptions.exn: The LHS of in_cons (_ \\in _ :: _) does not match any subterm of the goal

original: rewrite in_cons. move=> /orP[]. - move/eqP=> H_eq. subst n. move: Hnin. rewrite negb_or. move/andP=> [H_unsat _]. apply H_unsat. - move=> H_in. move: Huniq. rewrite (count_uniq_mem _ _ _ Huniq) in_cons (negbTE Hnin) eqbF_neg. move/andP=> [_ H_neq]. apply/eqP; apply neq_sym, H_neq.
